Class FFDataBaseAbstractType

    @Internal
public abstract class FFDataBaseAbstractType
extends java.lang.Object
    The FFData structure specifies form field data for a text box, check box, or drop-down list box.

    Class and fields descriptions are quoted from [MS-DOC] -- v20121003 Word (.doc) Binary File Format; Copyright (c) 2012 Microsoft Corporation; Release: October 8, 2012

    NOTE: This source is automatically generated please do not modify this file. Either subclass or remove the record in src/types/definitions.

    This class is internal. It content or properties may change without notice due to changes in our knowledge of internal Microsoft Word binary structures.

    (FFData结构为文本框、复选框或下拉列表框指定表单字段数据。类和字段描述引用自[MS-Doc] -- v20121003 Word（.Doc）二进制文件格式;版权所有（c）2012 Microsoft Corporation;发布日期：2012年10月8日注：此源是自动生成的，请不要修改此文件。可以子类或删除SRC/types/definition中的记录。这个类是内部的。由于我们对内部Microsoft Word二进制结构的了解发生了变化，其内容或属性可能会在不通知的情况下发生变化。)

      • getCch

        @Internal
public int getCch()
        An unsigned integer that specifies the maximum length, in characters, of the value of the textbox. This value MUST NOT exceed 32767. A value of 0 means there is no maximum length of the value of the textbox. If bits.iType is not iTypeText (0), this value MUST be 0..(一个无符号的integer，指定文本框值的最大长度（以字符为单位）。该值不得超过32767。值为0意味着文本框的值没有最大长度。如果bits.iType不是iTypext（0），则该值必须为0。)

      • getHps

        @Internal
public int getHps()
        An unsigned integer. If bits.iType is iTypeChck (1), hps specifies the size, in half-points, of the checkbox and MUST be between 2 and 3168, inclusive. If bits.iType is not iTypeChck (1), hps is undefined and MUST be ignored..(无符号整数。如果bits.iType为iTypChck（1），则hps指定复选框的大小（以零点为单位），并且必须在2和3168之间（含2和3168）。如果bits.iType不是iTypChck（1），则hps未定义并且必须忽略。)

      • setIRes

        @Internal
public void setIRes(byte value)
        Sets the iRes field value. An unsigned integer. If iType is iTypeText (0), then iRes MUST be 0. If iType is iTypeChck (1), iRes specifies the state of the checkbox and MUST be 0 (unchecked), 1 (checked), or 25 (undefined). Undefined checkboxes are treated as unchecked. If iType is iTypeDrop (2), iRes specifies the current selected list box item. A value of 25 specifies the selection is undefined. Otherwise, iRes is a zero-based index into FFData.hsttbDropList.(设置iRes字段值。无符号整数。如果iType为iTypext（0），则iRes必须为0。如果iType为iTypChck（1），则iRes指定复选框的状态，并且必须为0（未选中）、1（已选中）或25（未定义）。未定义的复选框被视为未选中。如果iType为iTypeDrop（2），则iRes指定当前选定的列表框项。值为25指定选择未定义。否则，iRes是FFTData.hsttbDropLists的从零开始的索引。)

      • getIRes

        @Internal
public byte getIRes()
        An unsigned integer. If iType is iTypeText (0), then iRes MUST be 0. If iType is iTypeChck (1), iRes specifies the state of the checkbox and MUST be 0 (unchecked), 1 (checked), or 25 (undefined). Undefined checkboxes are treated as unchecked. If iType is iTypeDrop (2), iRes specifies the current selected list box item. A value of 25 specifies the selection is undefined. Otherwise, iRes is a zero-based index into FFData.hsttbDropList.(无符号整数。如果iType为iTypext（0），则iRes必须为0。如果iType为iTypChck（1），则iRes指定复选框的状态，并且必须为0（未选中）、1（已选中）或25（未定义）。未定义的复选框被视为未选中。如果iType为iTypeDrop（2），则iRes指定当前选定的列表框项。值为25指定选择未定义。否则，iRes是FFTData.hsttbDropLists的从零开始的索引。)
        Returns:
        the iRes field value.(iRes字段值。)
